docs {
  ## List Cluster
  แสดงรายการคลัสเตอร์ทั้งหมดพร้อมการแบ่งหน้าและค้นหา

  Lists all hotel chains or company organizations registered in the platform, with filtering and pagination. Each cluster groups multiple business units (hotel properties) that share procurement and inventory management.

  ### Query Parameters
  | Name | Type | Required | Default | Description |
  |------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
  | `page` | number | No | 1 | Page number |
  | `perpage` | number | No | 10 | Items per page |
  | `search` | string | No | — | Search by name or code |
  | `version` | string | No | latest | API version |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  Platform admin only — managed at Keycloak realm role level

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": [
      {
        "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
        "code": "CL-001",
        "name": "Blueledgers Hotel Group",
        "alias_name": "BLG",
        "is_active": true,
        "max_license_bu": 10
      }
    ],
    "paginate": {
      "page": 1,
      "perpage": 10,
      "pages": 2,
      "total": 12,
      "prev": null,
      "next": 2
    },
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Missing or invalid bearer token |
}
